parameters:
Taking care of the statues is tough... And I... I'm small
and petite...

La~la~... Taking care of flowers is the most enjoyable time
for me...
\SE[74]Well, I guess it turned out this way...
Vega-chan... What a disappointment... You guys were spies...

I'm sorry... but I can't let you take it out. If possible, I
don't want to resort to violence. Could you hand it over to
me?

\SE[4]If I were to hand it over... \!\SE[3]Would my kind
master overlook it and forgive me?

Ah... Of course... I'll have you do special missions for the
rest of your life...

\SE[72]I'm relieved to hear that. \SE[31]Without hesitation,
I can send you to hell.

Scary... But we're outnumbered. I have plenty of private
soldiers prepared, though...

Capture her!! \.Try not to hurt her as much as
possible...!!!

\SE[90] (Tch... I was hoping to settle this peacefully...
\SE[19] Looks like there's no choice but to dispose of
you...)

\SE[22]Here I go! Cat!! \SE[21]Create an opening in the
encirclement and break through!!!

\SE[22]You filthy, disgraceful noble!! As the head of the
Lira family, I will pass judgment! \SE[19]Count your sins!!

Guh... Useless fools...!! But!! There's still a trump card
left!

Kukukuh... Are you scared? But don't worry, I won't kill you
or anything! I'll take care of everyone for the rest of
their lives...!!

What are these immature brats!! \! Act Schneider!! \. Take
care of them!!!

\SE[50]I never intended to train you all to be so weak that
you would be defeated by such small fry! \SE[22]Show Nikita
your growth... \SE[19]Show it to him!!
What...!? Act Schneider is... Could it be...!!?

\SE[20]... It seems like your tricks have run out. Well,
I'll let it end here for today! \SE[19] Tremble and wait for
the day of judgment to come!!
